Are you sure you want to delete all arti.msgid: Are you sure you want to delete all article drafts?
msgstr: 确定要删除所有文章草稿吗?

Are you sure you want to delete this art.msgid: Are you sure you want to delete this article?

Are you sure you want to delete this dra.msgid: Are you sure you want to delete this draft?
msgstr: 是否确实要删除此草稿?

Are you sure you want to delete this wor.msgid: Are you sure you want to delete this work item?
msgstr: 确定要删除此工作项吗?

By logging in, you agree to the Privacy.msgid: By logging in, you agree to the Privacy Policy.
msgstr: 登录，即表示您同意《隐私政策》。

Do you really want to log out?.msgid: Do you really want to log out?

Do you really want to remove this accoun.msgid: Do you really want to remove this account?

msgstr: 用于跟进的电子邮件地址

Enter the web address for a YouTrack ins.msgid: Enter the web address for a YouTrack installation where you have a registered account
msgstr: 输入您拥有注册帐户的 YouTrack 安装的网址

Filter projects, saved searches, and tag.msgid: Filter projects, saved searches, and tags
msgstr: 筛选项目、保存的搜索和标签
帮助我们更快地修正问题

Here you'll see a list of articles from.msgid: Here you'll see a list of articles from your favorite projects
msgstr: 您将在这里看到您收藏的项目的文章列表

If this isn't what you expected, you mig.msgid: If this isn't what you expected, you might try one of these solutions:
msgstr: 如果这不是您所期望的，您可以尝试以下解决方案之一:

In addition to our built-in error report.msgid: In addition to our built-in error reporting, YouTrack Mobile uses Bugsnag, a third-party service that helps us diagnose problems and monitor application stability. We only share report data with Bugsnag if you agree to allow us to do so.
msgstr: 除了我们内置的错误报告之外，YouTrack Mobile 还会使用第三方服务 Bugsnag，它可以帮助我们诊断问题并监控应用程序的稳定性。只有在您同意允许我们共享的情况下，我们才会与 Bugsnag 共享报告数据。

Issues can be sorted by up to 4 attribut.msgid: Issues can be sorted by up to 4 attributes
msgstr: 问题最多可以按 4 个特性进行排序

It could mean that the issue doesn't exi.msgid: It could mean that the issue doesn't exist or you don't have permission to view it
msgstr: 这可能意味着该问题不存在或者您没有权限查看它

No user information provided by Upsource.msgid: No user information provided by Upsource.
msgstr: Upsource 没有提供用户信息.
是否从收藏夹中移除项目?

Select an article from the list.msgid: Select an article from the list

Select an issue from the list.msgid: Select an issue from the list

msgstr: 向 Bugsnag 发送扩展报告
显示所有标记为“{{tagName}}”的问题…

The application failed to restart automa.msgid: The application failed to restart automatically. Please try to restart it manually.
msgstr: 应用程序无法自动重新启动。请尝试手动重新启动。

The author of this commit has not been i.msgid: The author of this commit has not been identified because they haven't specified their email address in their YouTrack profile.
msgstr: 此提交的作者尚未确定，因为他们没有在 YouTrack 个人资料中指定他们的电子邮件地址。

The change has been detached from this i.msgid: The change has been detached from this issue. It is still displayed here because its comment mentions the issue.
msgstr: 更改已从此问题分离。它仍然显示在这里，是因为它的注释提到了这个问题。

The change has been manually attached to.msgid: The change has been manually attached to this issue.
msgstr: 更改已手动附加到此问题。

The change was processed during the init.msgid: The change was processed during the initial data fetching, thus no command has been applied.
msgstr: 更改在初始数据获取期间处理，因此未应用任何命令。

The commit author does not belong to the.msgid: The commit author does not belong to the committers group.
msgstr: 提交作者不属于提交者群组。

The commit author has not specified an e.msgid: The commit author has not specified an email address.
msgstr: 提交作者未指定电子邮件地址.

The commit author has specified an email.msgid: The commit author has specified an email address that is associated with a different user account.
msgstr: 提交作者指定了与其他帐户关联的电子邮件地址.

The commit author is not an assignee in.msgid: The commit author is not an assignee in the project.
msgstr: 提交作者不是项目的被指派者。

The selected account is no longer author.msgid: The selected account is no longer authorized to use YouTrack Mobile. Please log in again.
msgstr: 所选帐户不再具备使用 YouTrack Mobile 的授权。请重新登录。

The server is overloaded or down for mai.msgid: The server is overloaded or down for maintenance
msgstr: 服务器已过载或者正在停机进行维护

The settings for this agile board have b.msgid: The settings for this agile board have been updated. Please reload the board.
msgstr: 此敏捷面板的设置已更新。请重新加载面板。

The VCS user name does not match any use.msgid: The VCS user name does not match any user in YouTrack. To link future commits, add the VCS user name to the Hub account for this user.
msgstr: VCS 用户名与 YouTrack 中的任何用户都不匹配。要链接未来的提交，请将 VCS 用户名添加到此用户的 Hub 帐户。

The VCS user name matches more than one.msgid: The VCS user name matches more than one user in YouTrack. To link future commits, remove the duplicate VCS user names from one or more Hub accounts or merge the duplicates into a single user account.
msgstr: VCS 用户名与 YouTrack 中的多个用户匹配。要链接未来的提交，请从一个或多个 Hub 帐户中删除重复的 VCS 用户名，或将重复的用户名合并到一个用户帐户中。

There was an error retrieving informatio.msgid: There was an error retrieving information about the change's author from TeamCity. The most probable reason is that TeamCity user that integration runs on behalf of does not have the required permissions.
msgstr: 从 TeamCity 检索有关更改作者的信息时出错。最可能的原因是代表集成运行的 TeamCity 用户没有所需的权限。

This action deletes all drafts, includin.msgid: This action deletes all drafts, including unpublished sub-articles
msgstr: 此操作将删除所有草稿，包括未发布的子文章

To view an item in context, select an is.msgid: To view an item in context, select an issue, article, or update from the list
msgstr: 要在上下文中查看条目，请从列表中选择问题、文章或更新

To view articles in the knowledge base f.msgid: To view articles in the knowledge base for a specific project, mark it as a favorite
msgstr: 要查看特定项目的知识库中的文章，请将其标记为收藏项

Touch and hold an item to view a list of.msgid: Touch and hold an item to view a list of available actions
msgstr: 轻触并按住条目可以查看可用操作列表

When integrating TeamCity and YouTrack,.msgid: When integrating TeamCity and YouTrack, the users are matched by their email addresses. TeamCity has not provided any email address of the committer.
msgstr: 当集成 TeamCity 和 YouTrack 时，会根据用户的电子邮件地址对用户进行匹配。TeamCity 没有提供提交者的任何电子邮件地址。

When integrating TeamCity and YouTrack,.msgid: When integrating TeamCity and YouTrack, the users are matched by their email addresses. There are two or more different YouTrack users that have the same email address as the commit's author has in TeamCity.
msgstr: 当集成 TeamCity 和 YouTrack 时，会根据用户的电子邮件地址对用户进行匹配。有两个或更多不同的 YouTrack 用户与提交的作者在 TeamCity 中拥有相同的电子邮件地址。

You don’t have any unread notifications.msgid: You don’t have any unread notifications

You haven't received any notifications y.msgid: You haven't received any notifications yet. To configure the notification preferences for your account, access your YouTrack profile in the web app.
msgstr: 您还没有收到任何通知。要为您的帐户配置通知偏好设置，请在 Web 应用中访问您的 YouTrack 个人资料。

You need a YouTrack account to use the a.msgid: You need a YouTrack account to use the app.
msgstr: 您需要 YouTrack 帐户才能使用该应用。

Your account has insufficient permission.msgid: Your account has insufficient permission to perform this operation.
msgstr: 您的帐户权限不足，无法执行此操作。

Your mobile device is running low on ava.msgid: Your mobile device is running low on available storage space. Some app functionality may be unavailable.
msgstr: 您的移动设备可用存储空间不足。某些应用功能可能不可用。

Your YouTrack account requires that you.msgid:
Your YouTrack account requires that you provide a second factor of authentication to log in. This option is only available when you log in with a mobile browser. The mobile browser will also let you sign in using a third-party account (if available).

To log in on this screen, enter your username and a one-time application password.
msgstr:
您需要提供第二重身份验证才能登录您的 YouTrack 帐户。此选项仅在您使用移动浏览器登录时可用。移动浏览器还允许您使用第三方帐户(如果可用)登录。

要在此屏幕上登录，请输入您的用户名和一次性应用程序密码。

YouTrack did not find a user that matche.msgid: YouTrack did not find a user that matches the user account in Bitbucket.
msgstr: YouTrack 找不到与之相匹配的 Bitbucket 帐户。

YouTrack did not find a user that matche.msgid: YouTrack did not find a user that matches the user account in GitHub.
msgstr: YouTrack 找不到与之相匹配的 GitHub 帐户。

YouTrack did not find a user that matche.msgid: YouTrack did not find a user that matches the user account in GitLab.
msgstr: YouTrack 找不到与之相匹配的 GitLab 帐户。

YouTrack did not receive an email addres.msgid: YouTrack did not receive an email address for the commit author from Bitbucket.
msgstr: YouTrack 没有从 Bitbucket 收到提交作者的电子邮件地址.

YouTrack did not receive an email addres.msgid: YouTrack did not receive an email address for the commit author from GitHub.
msgstr: YouTrack 没有从 GitHub 收到提交作者的电子邮件地址.

YouTrack did not receive an email addres.msgid: YouTrack did not receive an email address for the commit author from GitLab.
msgstr: YouTrack 没有从 GitLab 收到提交作者的电子邮件地址.

YouTrack did not receive user data for t.msgid: YouTrack did not receive user data for this commit author from Bitbucket.
msgstr: YouTrack 没有从 Bitbucket 收到此提交作者的用户数据.

YouTrack did not receive user data for t.msgid: YouTrack did not receive user data for this commit author from GitHub.
msgstr: YouTrack 没有从 GitHub 收到此提交作者的用户数据.

YouTrack did not receive user data for t.msgid: YouTrack did not receive user data for this commit author from GitLab.
msgstr: YouTrack 没有从 GitLab 收到此提交作者的用户数据.

YouTrack found multiple users with email.msgid: YouTrack found multiple users with email addresses that match the registered email in Bitbucket.
msgstr: YouTrack 发现多个用户的电子邮件地址与 Bitbucket 中注册的电子邮件地址相匹配.

YouTrack found multiple users with email.msgid: YouTrack found multiple users with email addresses that match the registered email in GitHub.
msgstr: YouTrack 发现多个用户的电子邮件地址与 GitHub 中注册的电子邮件地址相匹配.

YouTrack found multiple users with email.msgid: YouTrack found multiple users with email addresses that match the registered email in GitLab.
msgstr: YouTrack 发现多个用户的电子邮件地址与 GitLab 中注册的电子邮件地址相匹配.

YouTrack was unable to match the VCS use.msgid: YouTrack was unable to match the VCS user name to a Hub account for an unknown reason. Check your server logs for details.
msgstr: 由于未知原因，YouTrack 无法将 VCS 用户名与 Hub 帐户匹配。请查看您的服务器日志获取详细信息。
